<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>시저 하라다(Cesar Harada)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/cesar_harada_how_i_teach_kids_to_love_science?language=ko' lang='ko'>
아이들이 과학을 사랑하도록 가르치는 방법
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Oct 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Informative
</span>
</span>
</div>
